snippet.title: Gummy Bear Aqua Park 🏄 Gummibär Race Game Out Now! iOS & Android
snippet.description:
▶ Download on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/gummy-bear-aqua-park/id1609429031
▶ Download on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.unicogames.gummybear.aquapark

Download & Play the NEW Gummibär game - Gummy Bear Aqua Park! Jump into the pool and race your friends through the amazing 3D waterpark to all of your favorite Gummy songs! Can you set the high score?

Features:
- Amazing 3D Aqua Park with water slides
- Discover new tracks and race to all of your favorite Gummy Songs
- Tons of fun outfits and accessories to unlock
- Race your friends as the famous Gummy Bear, Gummibär!
- Play offline with no Wi-Fi needed

Gummy Bear Aqua Park is a GummyBear International Inc. Official Licensed Product.
